OL,3,CMichael Sheen and Bella Ramsey among
OL,4,CCelebrity Traitors 2026 line-up
OL,6,FWelsh actor Michael Sheen, EastEnders'
OL,7,FRoss Kemp and The Last Of Us star
OL,8,FBella Ramsey are among the famous
OL,9,Ffaces confirmed for the upcoming
OL,10,Fseries of Celebrity Traitors.
OL,12,FThe beloved BBC reality game show will
OL,13,Fsee 21 stars head to the Scottish
OL,14,Fcastle in the Highlands for the chance
OL,15,Fto win a cash prize of up to #100,000
OL,16,Ffor a charity of their choice.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
