OL,3,CMichael Sheen and Bella Ramsey among
OL,4,CCelebrity Traitors 2026 line-up
OL,6,FHosted by Claudia Winkleman, the game
OL,7,Ffollows the celebrity contestants `
OL,8,Fthe majority of whom are known as
OL,9,Ffaithfuls ` as they try to seek out
OL,10,Fthe murderous traitors among them, who
OL,11,Fkill off players in the middle of the
OL,12,Fnight.
OL,14,FThe broadcaster revealed its star-
OL,15,Fstudded line-up on Saturday ` which
OL,16,Fincludes Industry actress Myha'la
OL,17,FHerrold, who will join alongside model
OL,18,FJerry Hall and Saltburn actor Richard
OL,19,FE Grant.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
