OL,3,CMichael Sheen and Bella Ramsey among
OL,4,CCelebrity Traitors 2026 line-up
OL,6,FA number of comedians will also join
OL,7,Fthe second series of the spin-off show
OL,8,Fincluding James Acaster, Joe Lycett
OL,9,Fand Romesh Ranganathan ` as well as
OL,10,FRob Beckett and Joanne McNally.
OL,12,FThey will face singer-songwriter James
OL,13,FBlunt, former Little Mix star Leigh-
OL,14,FAnne Pinnock, actress Miranda Hart and
OL,15,FLove Island presenter Maya Jama in a
OL,16,Fbid to catch the treacherous traitors.
OL,18,FOthers joining the line-up include
OL,19,FCoronation street star Julie
OL,20,FHesmondhalgh, broadcaster Amol Rajan,
OL,21,Fand Scottish actress Sharon Rooney.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
