OL,3,CMichael Sheen and Bella Ramsey among
OL,4,CCelebrity Traitors 2026 line-up
OL,6,FBroadcaster and mathematician
OL,7,FProfessor Hannah Fry completes the
OL,8,Fline-up alongside content creator King
OL,9,FKenny and actor Sebastian Croft.
OL,11,FThe first series of The Celebrity
OL,12,FTraitors aired on the BBC last autumn,
OL,13,Fwith its nail-biting finale hitting a
OL,14,Fpeak of 15.4 million viewers,
OL,15,Faccording to the broadcaster.
