OL,3,CMichael Sheen and Bella Ramsey among
OL,4,CCelebrity Traitors 2026 line-up
OL,6,FIt featured a star-studded cast
OL,7,Fincluding actors Celia Imrie and Nick
OL,8,FMohammed, singer Paloma Faith, author
OL,9,Fand actor Sir Stephen Fry, broadcaster
OL,10,FJonathan Ross and comedian Alan Carr,
OL,11,Fwho went on to win as a Traitor.
OL,13,FThe spin-off series brought in an
OL,14,Faverage audience of 14.9 million
OL,15,Fpeople during its run ` the biggest TV
OL,16,Faudience of 2025.
